# ToolsHub — Frontend Environment Config
# -------------------------------------------------------
# This file documents frontend-level configuration.
# For Cloudflare Worker secrets (API keys etc.), see:
#   worker/.env.example  (use `wrangler secret put` — NOT .env files)
# -------------------------------------------------------

# NOTE: The frontend Worker API endpoint URL is centralized in js/config/api.js
# Do NOT set it here for the frontend; edit that file directly if the URL changes.

# WORKER_URL
# This environment variable is used ONLY by the offline RAG ingestion tool
# (`scripts/ingest.js`). It is not bundled or consumed by the web frontend.
# Example:
# WORKER_URL=https://toolshub-api-worker.theliquidlounge-co.workers.dev
